  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/803972c7b41b581271f74267fe940ed2.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=612 height=38 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/803972c7b41b581271f74267fe940ed2.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/803972c7b41b581271f74267fe940ed2.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/e8a438820c7a67093917d86db1abed04.avif?t=1734162718\" width=616 height=150 /></span>Get ready for an enigmatic and challenging adventure with O.W.L Projekt, a 3D isometric puzzle game that will test your mind and logic skills. Controlling Elysion, a young being created in a mysterious experiment, you will face the enigmatic Watchers in a journey to escape and uncover secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with the powerful Sanctum Staff, Elysion can move objects and overcome obstacles, offering a unique and immersive gaming experience. Challenge yourself through 50 meticulously designed levels, each featuring innovative mechanics and increasing difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/face10d3cdfc01bbf913b08436c50445.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/face10d3cdfc01bbf913b08436c50445.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/face10d3cdfc01bbf913b08436c50445.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/1f9b6918d53b2cf7390ed482056fcc13.avif?t=1734162718\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Innovative Puzzle Mechanics: Manipulate blocks, drag platforms, discover secret passages, and climb ladders in a 3D isometric environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progressive Challenges: Each set of levels introduces new challenges and mechanics, keeping the game always interesting and stimulating.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging Story: Follow Elysion on his mission to escape the Watchers, the mysterious guardians of the experimental project that created him.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Aesthetic: Enjoy a captivating visual style and intriguing level design.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 Exclusive Levels: Explore and solve puzzles in 50 distinct levels, each offering a unique and rewarding challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/85acbdd8e4bd4db48c25427953a6372c.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/85acbdd8e4bd4db48c25427953a6372c.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/85acbdd8e4bd4db48c25427953a6372c.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/2e6f221069ee6fcd13e3db7ac67f0c25.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/2e6f221069ee6fcd13e3db7ac67f0c25.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/2e6f221069ee6fcd13e3db7ac67f0c25.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Elysion escape and uncover the secrets behind his creation. Use the power of the Sanctum Staff to move mountains (literally) and overcome all the challenges in your path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/1356cdd153f04cbfdc24b2ed92b6a4dd.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/1356cdd153f04cbfdc24b2ed92b6a4dd.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/1356cdd153f04cbfdc24b2ed92b6a4dd.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to test your mind and logic? Embark on the adventure of O.W.L Projekt and see if you can unravel all the secrets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WISHLIST NOW</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/bb066ae061ea84ba2e96e31307d42fa6.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/bb066ae061ea84ba2e96e31307d42fa6.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/bb066ae061ea84ba2e96e31307d42fa6.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/803972c7b41b581271f74267fe940ed2.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=612 height=38 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/803972c7b41b581271f74267fe940ed2.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/803972c7b41b581271f74267fe940ed2.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/e8a438820c7a67093917d86db1abed04.avif?t=1734162718\" width=616 height=150 /></span>Get ready for an enigmatic and challenging adventure with O.W.L Projekt, a 3D isometric puzzle game that will test your mind and logic skills. Controlling Elysion, a young being created in a mysterious experiment, you will face the enigmatic Watchers in a journey to escape and uncover secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with the powerful Sanctum Staff, Elysion can move objects and overcome obstacles, offering a unique and immersive gaming experience. Challenge yourself through 50 meticulously designed levels, each featuring innovative mechanics and increasing difficulty.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/face10d3cdfc01bbf913b08436c50445.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/face10d3cdfc01bbf913b08436c50445.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/face10d3cdfc01bbf913b08436c50445.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/1f9b6918d53b2cf7390ed482056fcc13.avif?t=1734162718\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Innovative Puzzle Mechanics: Manipulate blocks, drag platforms, discover secret passages, and climb ladders in a 3D isometric environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progressive Challenges: Each set of levels introduces new challenges and mechanics, keeping the game always interesting and stimulating.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging Story: Follow Elysion on his mission to escape the Watchers, the mysterious guardians of the experimental project that created him.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Aesthetic: Enjoy a captivating visual style and intriguing level design.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 Exclusive Levels: Explore and solve puzzles in 50 distinct levels, each offering a unique and rewarding challenge.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/85acbdd8e4bd4db48c25427953a6372c.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/85acbdd8e4bd4db48c25427953a6372c.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/85acbdd8e4bd4db48c25427953a6372c.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/2e6f221069ee6fcd13e3db7ac67f0c25.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/2e6f221069ee6fcd13e3db7ac67f0c25.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/2e6f221069ee6fcd13e3db7ac67f0c25.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Elysion escape and uncover the secrets behind his creation. Use the power of the Sanctum Staff to move mountains (literally) and overcome all the challenges in your path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/1356cdd153f04cbfdc24b2ed92b6a4dd.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=610 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/1356cdd153f04cbfdc24b2ed92b6a4dd.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/1356cdd153f04cbfdc24b2ed92b6a4dd.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ready to test your mind and logic? Embark on the adventure of O.W.L Projekt and see if you can unravel all the secrets!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WISHLIST NOW</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/bb066ae061ea84ba2e96e31307d42fa6.poster.avif?t=1734162718\" width=600 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/bb066ae061ea84ba2e96e31307d42fa6.webm?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110690/extras/bb066ae061ea84ba2e96e31307d42fa6.mp4?t=1734162718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
